window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>There is something in the local cemetery that comes out at night. Something that is unearthing corpses and killing people. It’s the summer of 1984 and Timmy and his friends are looking forward to no school, comic books, and adventure. But instead they will be fighting for their lives.&nbsp;</p> <p>The ghoul has smelled their blood and it is after them.But that’s not the only monster they will face this summer....</p> <p>From award-winning horror master Brian Keene comes a novel of monsters, murder, and the loss of innocence.</p>"; 
